<p style=\"border:0px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:10px 0px 20px;font-size:16px;color:#191919;font-family:\" line-height:30px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span style=\"border:0px;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:16px;\">由于城市的更新迭代，许多老建筑由于功能更不上需求，基础设施的缺失同样需要更新改造。</span> 
</p>
<p style=\"border:0px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:10px 0px 20px;font-size:16px;color:#191919;font-family:\" line-height:30px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20170918/7983040bc1fc4685b9f495a89520e1b5.png\" max-width=\"600\" style=\"margin:10px auto 0px;padding:0px;display:block;max-width:100%;height:auto;\" /> 
